Text: Now 49° Wed 62° Thu 62° by Michael Turner UPDATE: SMYRNA, Tenn. -- Smyrna police haved located a missing woman who was last seen leaving a local bar. Police say, Engle made contact with law enforcement late last night. ------------- SMYRNA, Tenn. -- Smyrna police are searching for a missing woman last seen leaving a local bar. Police say, Brianna Marie Engle, 36, was last seen at Darlin's Bar on Monday, Feb. 22. Engle was last scene wearing a black jacket, black pants and black boots. Engle was also carrying a white duffel bag with pink owls on it. According to friends and family, Engle may suffer from depression. Engle is described as a white female, 5 feet tall, weighing 120 pounds, with green eyes and brown hair. Anyone with information regarding the whereabouts of Engle are asked to call Smyrna Police at 615-459-6644. 2026 Sinclair, Inc.
